      <title>Telegram創辦人表示一年內用戶將突破10億</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/telegram-platform-hit-1-bln-users-within-year-founder-says-2024-04-17/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Telegram 訊息應用程式是最受歡迎的社交媒體平台之一，其億萬富翁創始人 Pavel Durov 週二表示，隨著它像「森林大火」一樣蔓延，一年內月活躍用戶可能會突破10 億。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/telegram-platform-hit-1-bln-users-within-year-founder-says-2024-04-17/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 04:33:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
