      <title>蘋果執行長表示正在考慮在印尼設立製造工廠</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-ceo-says-looking-into-possibility-building-manufacturing-facility-2024-04-17/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[蘋果執行長週三在會見總統佐科威後表示，將考慮在印尼建立一家製造工廠，佐科威希望這家科技巨頭透過與國內公司合作來增加其本地含量。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-ceo-says-looking-into-possibility-building-manufacturing-facility-2024-04-17/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 03:46:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
